org.apache.freemarker.core

Interface ParsingAndProcessingConfiguration

  • All Superinterfaces:
    ParsingConfiguration, ProcessingConfiguration
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    TopLevelConfiguration
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    Configuration, Configuration.Builder, Configuration.ExtendableBuilder, MutableParsingAndProcessingConfiguration, TemplateConfiguration, TemplateConfiguration.Builder

    public interface ParsingAndProcessingConfiguration
extends ParsingConfiguration, ProcessingConfiguration
    Don't implement this interface yourself; use the existing implementation(s). This interface is the union of ProcessingConfiguration and ParsingConfiguration, which is useful for declaring types for values that must implement both interfaces.
